title: Episode 4 - Frank breaks down healthcare, technicals, and retail with his guests
itunes:title: Frank breaks down healthcare, technicals, and retail with his guests
description: In this week's Podcast, Frank talks technicals with Dan Fitzpatrick from stockmarketmentor.com  and retail with Kristin Bentz from the Talented Blonde. Rob Fannon from S&A's Phase I newsletter also drops by to talk about heathcare.
